---
/**
 * LinkedIn mark — official LaMinga asset (Contenus 2/SVG/LK), outlined + optimized.
 * Themed inline: the plate paints with `currentColor` (= the page --accent) and the "in" knockout
 * paints with --color-paper. Rendered inline (not <img>) so currentColor resolves against the link.
 */
